                </div>

                <div class="motion-card glass p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 text-center border border-white/10 hover:border-[#00D1FF]/30 animate__fadeInUp animate__animated animate__bounce animate__delay-2s">
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-6 text-[#00D1FF]">ü§ñ</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#64FFDA]">Tecnolog√≠a Avanzada</h3>
                    <p class="text-[#8892B0] leading-relaxed">Formaci√≥n en inteligencia artificial, rob√≥tica y nuevas tecnolog√≠as.</p>
